<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV118">
<l>colliṉunto ḻiṟkaṇunto ṭakkaṟāta vaṉpiṉu</l>
<l>mallunaṉpa kaliṉōṭu māṉamālai kālaiyu</l>
<l>mallināṇma larkkiḻatti nātapāta pōtiṉaip</l>
<l>pulliyuḷḷam vīḷvilātu pūṇṭumīṇṭa tillaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord of the Lady on a fresh lotus flower! [My] heart—</l>
<l>[overwhelmed] in words, deeds, and a love that does not get severed—</l>
<l>has clung to [Your] flower[-like] feet</l>
<l rend="indent">during the night with darkness and the morning with good light,</l>
<l>Without dropping, being tied [to them] and has not returned!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
